tip.text: Easily the best Burgerplace in town, possibly in the whole of Belgium! The Revolver is a crowd favourite. Finally a juicy, succulent, grilled quality beef patty with fresh & crunchy buns. coming back!

The Newaris are the indigenous race of Katmandu in Nepal. They own a unique culture and cuisine. This is the ONLY Newari Restaurant in Belgium. Don't miss the Sekuwan spiced mutton and momo dumplings!

tip.text: We found a 'Bar Italiano' by accident today. The owners, true blue Italians, serve authentic Italian coffee, desserts, crepes both sweet and savoury. Am so going to go back for a good cappuccino!

tip.text: They serve crispy suckling pig leitão here but only after 5pm. Very local eatery full of local colours. Amazing food. Service is brisk but friendly!
